，句子1月，句子2月……\r<br>\r<br>精品区，大半是清语的句子。\r<br>\r<br>延皓点开了句子4月。\r<br>\r<br>1日。感情的世界，没有谁对不起谁，只有谁不懂得珍惜谁。\r<br>\r<br>2日。自己选择的路，跪着也要走完。\r<br>\r<br>3日。如果爱不曾来过，如果梦不曾碎过，如果心不曾疼过，那么我，是否还是你认识的我？\r<br>\r<br>4日。拥有时，请选择珍惜；放弃时，请不要回头。\r<br>\r<br>5日。手中无剑，我无法保护你；手中有剑，我无法抱紧你。\r<br>\r<br>…………\r<br>\r<br>30日。天荒地老，也要找到属于自己的摩天轮。\r<br>\r<br>延皓皱了皱眉头，说：“这人的句子都好伤感啊，真不知道是怎样的一个人。”\r<br>\r<br>我点了点头，想起了一件事。\r<br>\r<br>随即，我的声音回荡在整个房间：\r<br>\r<br>“延皓，你没给我买奶兮啊啊啊啊啊！！！！！！”\u0018","author":"棉花糖的吻_L","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.5a3aa553.PMdC_Oh46jE48yl0PwtHbA&fr=pb","date":"2009-01-10 14:29","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":289,"title":"回复：回复：ORZ..","content":"sf~","author":"江户川绫子","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.574b664c.30cDok9HldwodkqdCIvGsQ&fr=pb","date":"2009-01-10 14:30","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":290,"title":"回复：回复：ORZ..","content":"额...........你没更文啦................子..............","author":"棉花糖的吻_L","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.5a3aa553.PMdC_Oh46jE48yl0PwtHbA&fr=pb","date":"2009-01-10 14:32","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":291,"title":"回复：回复：ORZ..","content":"糖~我正写作业~边玩边写","author":"江户川绫子","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.574b664c.30cDok9HldwodkqdCIvGsQ&fr=pb","date":"2009-01-10 14:40","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":292,"title":"回复：回复：ORZ..","content":"哦~~~~~~~~~子~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~好好玩(写)哦~~~~~~~~~~~!","author":"棉花糖的吻_L","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.5a3aa553.PMdC_Oh46jE48yl0PwtHbA&fr=pb","date":"2009-01-10 14:41","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":293,"title":"回复：回复：ORZ..","content":"我正为案件烦恼~","author":"江户川绫子","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.574b664c.30cDok9HldwodkqdCIvGsQ&fr=pb","date":"2009-01-10 14:43","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":294,"title":"回复：回复：ORZ..","content":"糖，昨天